  "body": "Consult with gnidan on specs for this. \n\n* truffle-config.js probably needs to have separate environments baked in; may be a breaking change depending on how we set it up (default to no environment to prevent breaking changes)\n\n* Really how we already built the L2 boxes, but would be nice to have it all in one file (be aware that Starknet may be a special case and consider elements that may be specific to it when designing this architecture)\n\n* Format may need to be shared with Ganache (as it needs to know the order networks needs to be started)\n\n\n** Declarative Deployments needs this finished to function fully as expected **",
